      "content": "thanks, that's a good start for the baseline. but my readers are actually all over the world. what if they're in places like Tokyo, Lagos, or Mumbai? should they still follow these exact same rules to be seen as \"high-class,\" or do they need to incorporate their own local styles/customs to stay professional, or is that considered less sophisticated in a global context?",
